pirate-cave.name: Pirate Cave
pirate-cave.description: ThePirate Caveis an very low-levelDungeondesigned for weak (level 1+) characters. The enemies and boss all have low health and damage output for this purpose. This dungeon is the main source ofPirate Rumconsumable, the untieredCorsair Ring.

forest-maze.name: Forest Maze
forest-maze.description: TheForest Mazeis an very low-leveldungeondesigned for weak (level 3+) characters. Enemies and the boss have low health and damage output but are slightly more threatening than those in thePirate Cave.

spider-den.name: Spider Den
spider-den.description: TheSpider Denis an low-leveldungeondesigned for weak (level 5+) characters. Monsters have relatively low health and do not deal too much damage. However, enemy quantity in this dungeon is significant.

forbidden-jungle.name: Forbidden Jungle
forbidden-jungle.description: TheForbidden Jungleis a low to medium-levelDungeondesigned for mid-level (level 10+) players. Monsters are somewhat more durable than previous dungeons and can put out some decent damage. Enemy quantity is somewhat high as well, but spaced out.

the-hive.name: The Hive
the-hive.description: The Hiveis a low to medium-level dungeon aimed at players level 10+. It is a source ofPotions of Dexterity,Bottled Honey, and two untiered items: theHoney Scepterand theOrb of Sweet Demise.

snake-pit.name: Snake Pit
snake-pit.description: TheSnake Pitis a low-medium level dungeon. Enemies found in this dungeon have moderate amounts of health and can be particularly strong and dangerous in groups. This dungeon is intended for medium level players.

sprite-world.name: Sprite World
sprite-world.description: TheSprite Worldis a low to medium-level dungeon intended for moderately powerful (level 20 unmaxed) characters. The enemies are weak and have low health but the boss can be dangerous.

magic-woods.name: Magic Woods
magic-woods.description: TheMagic Woodsis a low to medium-level dungeon that is home to a very large variety of fairy enemies.

candyland-hunting-grounds.name: Candyland Hunting Grounds
candyland-hunting-grounds.description: TheCandyland Hunting Groundsis medium-level dungeon that is rarely found but can be farmed indefinitely for loot. It is a source ofPotions of Defense, Attack, and Wisdom,gumballandRock Candyconsumables, and twountiered items: theCandy Ring,Candy-Coated ArmorandBubblegum Bucket. It is also the drop l

undead-lair.name: Undead Lair
undead-lair.description: TheUndead Lairis a mid-level dungeon that is a source ofPotions of Wisdom, the untieredDoom Bow,Wandering Souls Spell,Ring of Skeletal Specters,Spectral Swordand two pieces of theHollow King Necromancer ST Set,  and it is also another location where theTarot Card Packcan be found to get a chance to

toxic-sewers.name: Toxic Sewers
toxic-sewers.description: TheToxic Sewersis a medium-level dungeon that is a source ofPotions of Defense, theMurky Toxin, theVoid Blade, and the entireAcidified Assassin ST Set.

cursed-library.name: Cursed Library
cursed-library.drops_from: Guaranteed drop from Shady Sect Leader

mad-lab.name: Mad Lab
mad-lab.description: TheMad Labis a medium leveldungeonthat is a source ofPotions of Wisdom,Potions of Defense, the UTMad Scientist Sorcerer Setand the entireHorrific Sorcerer ST Set. It is also one of the locations where theTarot Card Packcan be found to get a chance to obtain anyone of theTarot Card Artifacts.

abyss-of-demons.name: Abyss of Demons
abyss-of-demons.description: TheAbyss of Demonsis a medium-level dungeon that is a staple source ofPotions of Vitalityfor many players. It is also the drop location of the untieredDemon Blade,Berserker’s Breastplate,Volcanic Sheathand the entireMagmatic Mystic ST Set. Additionally it is also a location where theTarot Card Packc

manor-of-the-immortals.name: Manor of the Immortals
manor-of-the-immortals.description: TheManor of the Immortalsis a medium to high-level dungeon designed for fairly powerful (level 20 with defense maxed) characters.

ocean-trench.name: Ocean Trench
ocean-trench.description: TheOcean Trenchis a high-level dungeon with an underwater theme. The dungeon is a source ofPotions of Mana, and is the main source of the untieredCoral Huntress UT Setand all pieces of theSlurp Scion Wizard ST Set.

the-crawling-depths.name: The Crawling Depths
the-crawling-depths.description: The Crawling Depthsis a high-level dungeon that is a much more difficult version of theSpider Den.

woodland-labyrinth.name: Woodland Labyrinth
woodland-labyrinth.description: TheWoodland Labyrinthis a high-level dungeon that is a much more difficult version of theForest Maze.

deadwater-docks.name: Deadwater Docks
deadwater-docks.description: TheDeadwater Docksis a high-level dungeon that is a much more difficult version of thePirate Cave.

mountain-temple.name: Mountain Temple
mountain-temple.description: TheMountain Templeis a high-level dungeon that is a source of variousstat increase potions(excludingMana). It is also the primary source of the four untiered items: theWand of the Fallen, theOrb of Aether, theJade Stormand theKaiken, along with the entireAkuma Slayer Samurai ST Set.

lair-of-draconis.name: Lair of Draconis

boss.name: Feargus the Obsidian Dragon / Feargus the Demented

lair-of-draconis.description: TheLair of Draconisis a high-level dungeon consisting of boss fights against five elemental dragons. It is a source of stat increase potions, untiered armors (Leaf Dragon Hide Armor,Water Dragon Silk Robe,Fire Dragon Battle Armor), theCelestial Blade, theVision of Draconis, it also houses the artifa

tomb-of-the-ancients.name: Tomb of the Ancients
tomb-of-the-ancients.description: TheTomb of the Ancientsis an high-level dungeon that drops the entirePriest of Geb ST Setand five untiered items.

the-nest.name: The Nest
other_notable_drops: Mark of the Killer Bee Queen
the-nest.description: The Nestis an extremely dangerous dungeon that is meant to be a much more difficult version ofThe Hive, and is the fourth “epic” dungeon released, afterDeadwater Docks,Woodland Labyrinth, andThe Crawling Depths, which were released in 2013. fungal-cavern.name: Fungal Cavern
fungal-cavern.description: TheFungal Cavernis an extremely dangerous dungeon that is the first part of the Abandoned Mineshaft, with theCrystal Cavernbeing the second part. This dungeon is one of theExaltationdungeons, boostingWisdom.

crystal-cavern.name: Crystal Cavern
crystal-cavern.description: TheCrystal Cavernis an extremely dangerous dungeon that is the second part of the Abandoned Mineshaft, with theFungal Cavernbeing the first. This dungeon is one of theExaltationdungeons, boostingWisdom.

lost-halls.name: Lost Halls
lost-halls.description: TheLost Hallsis an endgame dungeon designed to be among the hardest content in the game. In addition to the main dungeon, there are 2 sub-areas: theCultist HideoutandThe Void, each with their own boss. Details about each sub-area can be found on their respective page. the-void.name: The Void
the-void.drops_from: Must useVial of Pure Darknessto open
the-void.description: The Voidis an endgame dungeon that is a sub-area of theLost Hallsand consists entirely of a boss fight against theVoid Entity. This dungeon is one of theExaltationdungeons, boostingMana.

the-shatters.name: The Shatters
the-shatters.description: The Shattersis an extremely dangerous and lengthy dungeon, intended to be approximately the hardest dungeon in the game beforeOryx’s Sanctuary, although its difficulty is commonly viewed as surpassing the dungeon in question. oryx-s-castle.drops_from: Automatically transported into it 2 minutes after Realm closes

wine-cellar.name: Wine Cellar
wine-cellar.drops_from: Locked portal is a guaranteed dropMust be opened with aWine Cellar Incantation
wine-cellar.description: TheWine Cellaris a high-level dungeon that can be accessed after defeatingOryx the Mad GodinOryx’s Chamber. Upon Oryx’s defeat, he will drop a Locked Wine Cellar Portal, which can be unlocked with aWine Cellar Incantation(or “inc”), an item that drops from most dungeon bosses. The portal will unlock

oryx-s-sanctuary.name: Oryx's Sanctuary
oryx-s-sanctuary.drops_from: Oryx the Mad God 2 is guaranteed to drop three monuments that must be activated with theOryx Runesfor the Oryx’s Sanctuary portal to appear.

battle-for-the-nexus.name: Battle for the Nexus
battle-for-the-nexus.description: Battle for the Nexusis a dungeon originally released for a limited time in September 2013.  After a security breach in the game, the developers created the dungeon as a kind of apology to the players, and the design echos the fight that players had to clear the Nexus of enemies.
